entities.name: ElizaOS
entities.description: An open-source framework for AI agent development. It focuses on providing infrastructure for autonomous AI-driven projects.

entities.name: Auto.fun
entities.description: A platform designed to serve as comprehensive infrastructure for AI-driven autonomous projects, expanding beyond initial concepts of token launches into broader AI agent-managed operations.

entities.name: Discord
entities.description: A communication platform offering voice, video, and text communication tailored for communities and gamers. It allows users to join servers and interact in channels.

entities.name: Trusted Execution Environment
entities.description: A secure area within a main processor where sensitive data can be processed. It ensures that code and data are protected from unauthorized access during execution.

entities.name: RAG
entities.description: Retrieval-Augmented Generation is a technique used in natural language processing to improve the quality of generated text by retrieving relevant information from external knowledge bases before generating a response.

entities.name: Notion
entities.description: A workspace application that combines note-taking, project management, and database functionalities. It allows users to create and organize information in various formats.

entities.name: Twitter/X
entities.description: A social media platform that allows users to post and interact with short messages. It has undergone changes related to its API access and pricing.

entities.name: Strapi
entities.description: An open-source headless Content Management System (CMS) that enables developers to easily manage and deliver content across various platforms.

entities.name: Directus
entities.description: A real-time API for any SQL database, providing a headless CMS and application platform. It offers a flexible way to manage content and build digital experiences.

entities.name: Sanity
entities.description: A headless CMS platform that provides real-time content management and a structured approach to building digital products. It allows for flexible content modeling and delivery.

entities.name: Solana
entities.description: A high-performance blockchain platform designed to support decentralized applications and cryptocurrencies. It aims to offer scalability and fast transaction processing.

entities.name: EVM
entities.description: Ethereum Virtual Machine is the runtime environment for smart contracts on the Ethereum blockchain. It is a Turing-complete virtual machine that executes bytecode.
